OF SOME OTHER KIND OF BOND.

14
00:02:41,083 --> 00:02:43,291
- AH, DO YOU PRACTICE
BEING A MORON?

15
00:02:43,375 --> 00:02:45,666
- SHUT UP. 
NO ONE ASKED YOU.

16
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,000
- WHY, YOU JERK.

17
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:49,416
- DON'T TROUBLE YOURSELF.
THERE'S NOTHING TO FEAR.

18
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,625
WE'LL ARRIVE IN
OUR OWN GOOD TIME.

19
00:02:51,708 --> 00:02:54,375
BELIEVE ME, KEIRO WILL MOST
LIKELY BE WAITING FOR US.

20
00:02:54,458 --> 00:02:56,583
IT'S YOUR DESTINY. THAT SAID,

21
00:02:56,666 --> 00:02:58,916
THE QUESTION YOU SHOULD BE
ASKING IS WHETHER YOU'RE

22
