TO FACE HIM.

23
00:03:00,333 --> 00:03:03,083
- FACE HIM? HEY, HOLD ON.

24
00:03:03,166 --> 00:03:05,541
THE ONLY REASON HE BEAT ME
IS 'CAUSE I WAS TIRED

25
00:03:05,625 --> 00:03:08,208
AND HE CAUGHT ME OFF GUARD.
IF IT'D BEEN A FAIR FIGHT HE...

26
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,791
- WHAT DID I TELL YOU?
THERE'S NO SUCH THING

27
00:03:09,875 --> 00:03:11,041
AS A FAIR FIGHT.

28
00:03:11,125 --> 00:03:12,500
YOU'D BEST LEARN THAT.

29
00:03:12,583 --> 00:03:15,333
IN THE MEANTIME, I SUGGEST
WE TRAVEL AT OUR LEISURE.

30
00:03:15,416 --> 00:03:17,833
BESIDES, THIS IS A GOOD SPOT
TO WASH UP.

31
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,208
- ( humming )

32
00:03:35,333 --> 00:03:37,583
- SO, YOU REALLY THINK
I'VE GOT MY WORK CUT OUT

33
00:03:37,666 --> 00:03:38,875
FOR ME, DON'T YOU?

34
00:03:38,958 --> 00:03:40,166
- LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

35
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:42,875
YOU DO KNOW THE EIGHT
GREAT STYLES, YES?

36
00:03:42,958 --> 00:03:45,291
- OF COURSE, I WAS RAISED
BY THE PRIESTHOOD.

37
00:03:45,375 --> 00:03:48,416
- VERY WELL. THEN WHAT EXACTLY
ARE THEY? NAME THEM ALL OFF.

38
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:50,458
- AH. YOU'VE GOT THE FIST,

39
00:03:50,541 --> 00:03:53,166
AND YOU'VE GOT THE STAFF
THEN THE ROPE, THE BOW,

40
00:03:53,250 --> 00:03:56,041
THE SPEAR, THERE'S THE SWORD
THEN THERE'S THE...

41
