AS CHANNELING.

47
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,833
- CHANNELING? WHAT'S THAT?

48
00:04:09,916 --> 00:04:11,666
- OF THE TWO, TRAGICALLY,

49
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:13,416
THE OLDEST STYLE IS NOW LOST
TO US.

50
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,416
