FEW PEOPLE WERE ABLE

51
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:17,083
TO MASTER IT.

52
00:04:17,166 --> 00:04:18,583
- AH. WHO CARES?

53
00:04:18,666 --> 00:04:20,500
COME ON, I'M NOT HERE
FOR A STUPID HISTORY LESSON.

54
00:04:20,583 --> 00:04:22,833
WHAT DOES ANY OF THIS HAVE
TO DO WITH ME? HEY, WAIT,

55
00:04:22,916 --> 00:04:24,291
DON'T JUST WALK AWAY.

56
00:04:24,375 --> 00:04:26,333
I WANT TO HEAR WHY YOU THINK
I CAN'T DEFEAT LORD KEIRO.

57
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:31,166
- ( grunts )

58
00:04:31,250 --> 00:04:33,083
- ( gasps ) MY WORD.

59
00:04:35,083 --> 00:04:38,291
- THAT, FRIENDS, IS CHANNELING.
NOT THE BEST EXAMPLE.

60
00:04:38,375 --> 00:04:39,833
CLOTH IS A POOR CONDUIT.

61
00:04:39,916 --> 00:04:42,833
BUT I'M SURE YOU GET
THE BASIC SENSE.

62
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:46,000
INCIDENTALLY, IT MAY INTEREST
YOU TO KNOW, KEIRO'S REPUTATION

63
00:04:46,083 --> 00:04:48,791
AS A CHANNELER IS UNMATCHED.

64
00:04:48,875 --> 00:04:51,541
TAITO, UNTIL A WARRIOR
LEARNS SELF-CONTROL,

65
