CHANNELING. DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

68
00:04:58,458 --> 00:05:01,416
- HMM. GIVE ME A BREAK.
HOW HARD COULD THIS BE?

69
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,583
WORK YOU PIECE OF CRAP.

70
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:05,166
- PATIENCE IS NOT HIS
STRONG POINT.

71
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,458
- ( grunts )

72
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:13,000
- ( chuckles ) THAT THING
IS COLOSSAL.

73
00:05:15,125 --> 00:05:19,208
- THE WO JIN SQUAD. WHAT BRINGS
THEM TO SUCH A RURAL PORT?

74
00:05:29,666 --> 00:05:32,541
- WOW. THIS IS
INCREDIBLE, TAI.

75
00:05:32,625 --> 00:05:35,291
