WHO LIKES TO HEDGE HIS BETS.

161
00:09:13,791 --> 00:09:18,083
- ( laughs ) YOU ARE
A PIECE OF WORK.

162
00:09:18,166 --> 00:09:20,125
MORE FOOD AND DRINK
FOR MY GOOD FRIEND,

163
00:09:20,208 --> 00:09:21,875
THE WATER-FARING SOOTHSAYER.

164
00:09:21,958 --> 00:09:24,125
- AS YOU WISH.

165
00:09:24,208 --> 00:09:26,083
- CARE FOR SOME
LIGHT ENTERTAINMENT?

166
00:09:26,166 --> 00:09:26,958
- HUH?

167
00:09:27,041 --> 00:09:29,333
- MY SPECIALTY, ONE OF SEVERAL.

168
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,500
- ( screams )

169
00:09:33,583 --> 00:09:35,291
- ( people cheering )

170
00:09:35,375 --> 00:09:36,875
- FORGIVE ME,
I'M A BIT OUT OF PRACTICE.

171
00:09:36,958 --> 00:09:39,000
- BAH, IT WAS SPLENDID.

172
00:09:39,083 --> 00:09:41,333
- HMM.
- DID YOU SEE, KORIN?

173
00:09:41,416 --> 00:09:44,041
- THE FAMOUS CAPTAIN
OF THE WO JIN SQUAD.

174
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:46,291
A VERY GOOD SIGN,
DON'T YOU AGREE?

175
00:09:46,375 --> 00:09:49,375
- QUITE. KOYO'S REPUTATION
DOES PRECEDE HIM, SIR.

176
00:09:49,458 --> 00:09:51,666
AND HE SEEMS EAGER
TO BE AT YOUR DISPOSAL.

177
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:53,500
- WHAT HAVE I ALWAYS TOLD YOU?

178
00:09:53,583 --> 00:09:55,791
POWER FOREVER GRAVITATES
TOWARDS POWER.

179
00:09:55,875 --> 00:09:57,500
- INDEED.

180
00:09:57,583 --> 00:09:58,541
- MY RETURN MUST BE GRAND.

181
00:09:58,625 --> 00:10:00,833
I'LL SPARE ABSOLUTELY
NO EXPENSE.

182
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:02,666
BID FAREWELL TO OBSCURITY.

183
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,000
AND TAKE WITH ME
WHAT RICHES

184
