THIS STAGNANT
BACKWATER STILL HOLDS.

185
00:10:06,458 --> 00:10:07,666
- ( chuckles )

186
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:23,666
- TROUBLE SLEEPING?

187
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,375
- ( screams )

188
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:27,916
- THERE'S A CORNER OF THE
COURTYARD THAT'S RELATIVELY DRY.

189
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:31,291
IDEAL FOR KEEPING
ONE SELF SHARP.

190
00:10:31,375 --> 00:10:33,041
FEEL FREE TO USE IT.

191
00:10:33,125 --> 00:10:36,541
- OKAY. SHE'S A NICE PERSON.
REMEMBER THAT.

192
00:10:41,916 --> 00:10:44,208
CHANNELING BEGINS WITH BEING
CONSCIOUS OF THE BODY'S

193
00:10:44,291 --> 00:10:46,333
NATURAL FLOW OF ENERGY.

194
00:10:46,416 --> 00:10:48,458
THE TRICK IS TO REDIRECT
THAT FLOW.

195
00:10:48,541 --> 00:10:50,916
THEN, LET YOUR
WEAPON DO THE REST.

196
00:10:54,333 --> 00:10:55,458
( grunts )

197
00:10:57,666 --> 00:11:01,416
