TO LET IT FLOW INTO THIS?

207
00:11:21,666 --> 00:11:23,458
IT'S JUST A STUPID RAG.

208
00:11:23,541 --> 00:11:24,833
- TO DEFEAT KEIRO,

209
00:11:24,916 --> 00:11:27,041
